{"tid":1374902,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"真心請教，戴眼鏡既人應該要用邊款眼罩","createTime":"2019-07-28T02:11:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T08:35:56.000Z","uid":40845,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ba4bcc144f6cf2f4235060712927bc78b53a2465","tid":1374902,"uid":40845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:11:53.000Z","msg":"真心想請教，問啲五金佬，已經同佢地講錢唔係問題既前提下，喺戴眼鏡既情況下邊款最好，可以包曬成對眼，結果話3m嗰隻已經好得，結果一上前線食撚曬，要即刻撤退。<br />\n又試過戴雪鏡。結果包唔曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />諗住戴con啦，結果去到前線有戰友話唔好戴仲危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真心想知，有邊隻係可以喺戴眼鏡既情況下可以保護好對眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d43b2e4b69b2fc261e2dc94c95b419fcb00f1668","tid":1374902,"uid":277286,"like":10,"dislike":3,"score":7,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:15:42.000Z","msg":"戴有度數嘅泳鏡"},{"pid":"d015d779eef29cf3bb91dac327d47e83212f74ff","tid":1374902,"uid":102224,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:16:03.000Z","msg":"有度數泳鏡？"},{"pid":"d14a9376669a475252864a85aac96e03cc478c7e","tid":1374902,"uid":50347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:21:26.000Z","msg":"泳鏡係無得輸"},{"pid":"4af85c6a5983a893621700fcf6795b620336b4e2","tid":1374902,"uid":277286,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:26:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.intl.taobao.com/detail/detail.html?id=563782351524&amp;spm=a21wu.10013511-tw.7.1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.intl.taobao.com%2Fdetail%2Fdetail.html%3Fid%3D563782351524%26spm%3Da21wu.10013511-tw.7.1&d=ajJRCbjZ3CJF8zdY8%2Fu%2F1x3udkpk2VnOHMKOPHAv%2FIQ%3D&h=b7ae7767\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.intl.taobao.com/detail/detail.html?id=563782351524&amp;spm=a21wu.10013511-tw.7.1</a>"},{"pid":"2d4c7587dcef73ecbc66ae1227efa3f87422a968","tid":1374902,"uid":277286,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T02:27:0